{"tid":912862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(NOW) 建制派民調: 陳凱欣大勝李卓人, 馮檢基第三","createTime":"2018-11-23T03:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T03:10:25.000Z","uid":134071,"like":23,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e20425abfb55f1e84f90cfb65627a1ccb343e2fe","tid":912862,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:50:59.000Z","msg":"建制派民意通常俾民調低佔.  今次陳凱欣係民調贏埋, 基本上肯定贏硬, 準備做議員. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n(香港研究協會係建制派組織)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=328213&amp;fbclid=IwAR29DULjNJWmJ582eoKB_wZiJ5t3cgVrzpGpgLaaDWxi4KRppbNTGxMwhWY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D328213%26fbclid%3DIwAR29DULjNJWmJ582eoKB_wZiJ5t3cgVrzpGpgLaaDWxi4KRppbNTGxMwhWY&d=GjAYn5dUZSke43U%2BKahIaTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=7d94444f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D328213%26fbclid%3DIwAR29DULjNJWmJ582eoKB_wZiJ5t3cgVrzpGpgLaaDWxi4KRppbNTGxMwhWY&h=fc845cf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=328213&amp;fbclid=IwAR29DULjNJWmJ582eoKB_wZiJ5t3cgVrzpGpgLaaDWxi4KRppbNTGxMwhWY</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/WtpoHED.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWtpoHED.jpg&h=b0d4d993&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民調顯示陳凱欣支持率稍為領先<br />\n13小時前<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】立法會九龍西補選星期日舉行，香港研究協會的民調顯示，陳凱欣支持率稍為領先。<br />\n<br />\n香港研究協會本月6至21日隨機以電話訪問超過1000名九龍西選民，問他們如果明天是補選，會投票給哪位候選人。有26%被訪者稱會投票給獲建制派支持的陳凱欣，領先民主派推薦的李卓人兩個百分點，支持率排第三的是馮檢基有11%，曾麗文及伍廸希支持率分別有5%或以下，而未決定投票取向或無意見的選民合共有超過三成。<br />\n<br />\n調查又問到選民認為今次補選是否重要，七成選民認為比較重要或非常重要，兩成人認為普通。而在另一條問題超過五成二選民表示一定會在補選中投票。"},{"pid":"7df340c173188ef448c947e96b31a7ffa6e32c2b","tid":912862,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:52:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25871582da396f8a133cf662c6f24ed74223db82","tid":912862,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af8ee82478e3c2291c970074d9c3aefb39195a8","tid":912862,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:04:24.000Z","msg":"陳凱欣開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8efb44838e3fad77f56d4ca720d7a3d2cd5dbf3d","tid":912862,"uid":85223,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:12:31.000Z","msg":"駛咩研究<br />\n贏硬啦<br />\n咁多高官親建支持都唔贏就死左佢啦"},{"pid":"055fbf5de6151e8c55f16bd3f2c81879b68f2f87","tid":912862,"uid":73200,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:13:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b513cb29f6d86855af93beb091f916f6e9423c3","tid":912862,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":60,"score":-59,"quote":{"pid":"8efb44838e3fad77f56d4ca720d7a3d2cd5dbf3d","tid":912862,"uid":85223,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:12:31.000Z","msg":"駛咩研究<br />\n贏硬啦<br />\n咁多高官親建支持都唔贏就死左佢啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:13:53.000Z","msg":"講真,佢好過李卓人, 馮檢基<br />\n<br />\n(雖然三個都係屎)"},{"pid":"e2619b306b6f4f7add477c247ef0047cd7894358","tid":912862,"uid":59283,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:14:45.000Z","msg":"咁都輸真係可以切腹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e03b753b8e61c454ccd77f0d417d653ba991317","tid":912862,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63540a5ef1bba525a3dc702ebaab6540efab2a4f","tid":912862,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg